channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Newsom's American Vision: Rubio's Closes 48 Locations Due to 'Rising Cost of Doing Business' in CA
Hunter Biden trial enters 3rd day with cross-examination of FBI agent
item.description: Hunter Biden's criminal trial held its second day in court, where jurors heard excerpts from Biden's memoir detailing his drug addiction as well as text messages he sent in 2018.

item.title: Hunter Biden's Ex-wife to Testify About Drug Use at Trial
item.description: The ex-wife of President Joe Biden's son Hunter Biden is expected to testify Wednesday about the younger Biden's drug use, which prosecutors contend he lied about to illegally buy a gun.

item.title: Biggs Absolutely Levels Garland, Blows Up the Excuses Not to Turn Over Hur Audio
Taiwan watches Ukraine for lessons on possible war with China
item.description: Taiwan is taking lessons on both strategy and how to handle its allies from Ukraine as it continues to fight a Russian invasion.

item.title: Rep. Jordan to Newsmax: Garland Doesn't Understand America
item.description: Among the most frightening revelations of Attorney General Merrick Garland's testimony on Tuesday is that he doesn't understand that the United States was founded on the idea that the people have a right to question their government, Rep. Jim Jordan, R-Ohio, said.

item.title: If Your Day Is Gone, and You Want to Ride On: Hunter Biden's Delaware Trial - Day 2
Conservative legal watchdog sues DOJ for records related to key figure in NY v Trump case
item.description: America First Legal is taking the Justice Department to court over its failure to furnish documents related to Matthew Colangelo, a key prosecutor in the NY v. Trump trial.

item.title: Son of Embattled Sen. Menendez Wins N.J. Dem House Primary
item.description: Rep. Rob Menendez, D-N.J., overcame the obstacle of the criminal charges involving his father, Sen. Robert Menendez, defeated Hoboken, New Jersey, Mayor Ravi Bhalla to win his Democrat primary Tuesday night.

item.title: LIVE: Election Results: D.C., Iowa, Montana, New Jersey, New Mexico, South Dakota
Biden displays signs of decline in private meetings with congressional leaders: Report
item.description: President Biden has shown signs of poor cognitive ability at times in private meetings with congressional leaders, but the White House maintains the he is still sharp and effective.

item.title: Idaho Bar Owner to Newsmax: Hetero Month About Faith
item.description: The bar owner who named June "Hetero Awesomeness Month" at his establishment in Eagle, Idaho, told Newsmax on Tuesday his promotion was about celebrating his "belief system," not someone else's.

item.title: 'Fungal Infection': Sen. Kennedy Lays Waste to Biden's Border Crisis Desperation in Must-Watch Takedown
State Auditor Troy Downing wins GOP primary for Montana seat held by Rep. Matt Rosendale
item.description: State Auditor Troy Downing won the Republican nomination in the race for Montana's 2nd Congressional District, a seat currently held by Rep. Matt Rosendale.

item.title: Karoline Leavitt to Newsmax: Biden's New Policy Puts America Last
item.description: Karoline Leavitt, national press secretary for Donald Trump’s presidential campaign, told Newsmax on Tuesday the furthest thing from President Joe Biden’s mind regarding his immigration policy is the safety and security of Americans.
